ivardefs.name: entry_
ivardefs.desc: An entry in a bundle resource - will either contain a resource or information about a resource (transactions and history only).

ivardefs.name: identifier
ivardefs.desc: A persistent identifier for the bundle that won't change as a bundle is copied from server to server.

ivardefs.name: link_
ivardefs.desc: A series of links that provide context to this bundle.

ivardefs.name: signature
ivardefs.desc: Digital Signature - base64 encoded. XML-DSig or a JWT.

ivardefs.name: timestamp
ivardefs.desc: The date/time that the bundle was assembled - i.e. when the resources were placed in the bundle.

ivardefs.name: total
ivardefs.desc: If a set of search matches, this is the total number of entries of type 'match' across all pages in the search.  It does not include search.mode = 'include' or 'outcome' entries and it does not provide a count of the number of entries in the Bundle.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: Indicates the purpose of this bundle - how it is intended to be used.

properties.desc: A container for a collection of resources.
